# Assets Loans And Receivables Current Total Calls And Other DRF 300 Amount

## identifier
de9038

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of calls and other receivables as required on DRF_300, classified as current in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.CurrentTotalCallsAndOtherDRF300.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.06
- period=instant
